<p><strong>阅读举报须知</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/760a218550b244458e8f13c97252f266.png" /></p>
<p><strong>5</strong></p>
<p><strong>选择举报类型、填写相关信息</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/2441bccdeae74e9e9eb7b6b3be576bf6.png" /></p>
